## Architectural Decisions (Bulleted)

**Decisions:**
- Individual QSL researchers *can* participate in ProQure vendor bids — the question is which ones, under what conditions, not whether
- The principle is **function-based exclusion** (what you do at QSL) not **employment-based exclusion** (who pays your salary)
